    <div data-cid="1196870">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1196870">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ligne/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1206785-132.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ligne/" class="name">黎戈</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2007-08-20" class="main-meta">2007-08-20 20:12:02</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1196870/">偶然之书</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1196870_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1196870">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        还在看&lt;神谕之夜&gt;。真迷人。每个情节的转角都是偶然，熟极而流的蒙太奇跳接。查了下资料,保罗.奥斯特君果然是有电影业从业经验的人。当过戛纳影展评委，还曾和香港导演王颖合作数次。1990年，《柏林苍穹下》的导演威姆•文德斯邀他就《马耳他之鹰》里的一个段子合导一部电影...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1196870-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1196870_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1196870_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

